<div class="sectionHeading">Placements</div>
<div class="card-body sectionContent">
<p>JECRC Foundation has set an exemplary record in engineering placements with its students being chosen by industry leaders, year after year. 620+ renowned companies have made more than 9500 offers to students in last 15 years. This year has been exceptional for JECRC umbrella in terms of placements. More than 1000+ offers have been rolled by reputed organizations like Accenture, Mindtree, IBM, Deloitte, Ericsson, HSBC Software, Capgemini, Hexaware Technologies, Sopra, Ernst & Young, Matrix Comsec, SkillRock Technologies, Newgen Software, Pinnacle Infotech, Liugong India, J.K. Cement Works, FEV India, Asahi Glass India Ltd., Zycus, etc.  JECRC Foundation have big infrastructure that holds the capacity of accommodating huge pool campus drive. Enough computer labs to conduct online test supporting the latest and high speed bandwidth internet facility. Fully equipped Auditorium, Board Room, Group Discussion Halls and exclusive air conditioned interview location at all JECRC Foundation campuses. We have hosted a several huge pooled campus recruitment drive successfully with participation of around 1800-5000 students for the various mass recruitment companies viz. Accenture, Delloite, Appirio, Tata Consultancy Services, Tech Mahindra etc.</p>

